00:09:08.115 --> 00:09:09.917 position:27% line:83% align:start
to the next stage
of your career.

00:09:10.084 --> 00:09:11.085 position:41% line:89% align:start
Got it!

00:09:11.218 --> 00:09:13.087 position:16% line:83% align:start
