for a second.

00:09:15.156 --> 00:09:17.825 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Look, she's glowing!
-Hmm?

00:09:18.359 --> 00:09:21.195 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TAKATSUKASA] You're Shinozaki
from Dev Group Two, right?

00:09:21.595 --> 00:09:22.897 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Yes.
-I make a point

00:09:23.030 --> 00:09:24.999 position:33% line:83% align:start
to keep tabs
on Group Two's hires.

00:09:25.499 --> 00:09:28.235 position:7% line:83% align:start
