00:12:50.404 --> 00:12:52.072 position:30% line:83% align:start
All right kids,
be sure to thank

00:12:52.206 --> 00:12:54.975 position:7% line:83% align:start
these nice people for bringing
in all these toys for us!

00:12:55.309 --> 00:12:57.878 position:33% line:83% align:start
[WALLA KIDS]
Thank you very much!

00:12:59.113 --> 00:13:02.116 position:16% line:83% align:start
-This one's my favorite.
-Me too!

00:13:02.416 --> 00:13:03.817 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
We can all go together.

00:13:04.251 --> 00:13:06.020 position:35% line:83% align:start
[GIRL 10F]
Draw me a Kyapicure, please!

00:13:06.153 --> 00:13:07.788 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[HAYAKAWA] All right.
-I want Meowjiro!

00:13:07.921 --> 00:13:09.123 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, sure thing!

00:13:09.256 --> 00:13:10.759 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Do one riding a bike!
-Coming right up!

00:13:10.891 --> 00:13:12.793 position:13% line:83% align:start
The kids look like they're
all having an awesome time!

00:13:12.926 --> 00:13:13.961 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're right!

00:13:14.795 --> 00:13:17.898 position:10% line:83% align:start
I had no idea that we oversaw
product tests like this.

00:13:18.098 --> 00:13:19.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's a pretty big part
of how we learn

00:13:19.800 --> 00:13:21.068 position:16% line:89% align:start
what adjustments to make.

00:13:21.268 --> 00:13:23.137 position:13% line:83% align:start
But we don't get to do this
very often,

00:13:23.270 --> 00:13:24.773 position:10% line:89% align:start
so be sure to pay attention.

00:13:25.372 --> 00:13:27.776 position:19% line:83% align:start
It might help you with
your project for the contest.

00:13:27.908 --> 00:13:29.143 position:38% line:89% align:start
Will do!

00:13:29.678 --> 00:13:30.911 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
The contest.

00:13:31.646 --> 00:13:32.681 position:30% line:89% align:start
What'll you do?

00:13:32.946 --> 00:13:34.081 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh.

00:13:34.348 --> 00:13:36.317 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, I wouldn't want
to make her worry.

00:13:37.451 --> 00:13:40.854 position:13% line:83% align:start
I ended up not telling her
or Manager about the wager yet.

00:13:41.922 --> 00:13:43.591 position:19% line:89% align:start
I have to say, though.

00:13:44.258 --> 00:13:45.760 position:35% line:83% align:start
[GIRL 10H]
Play with me! Play with me!

00:13:45.893 --> 00:13:47.394 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
What game should we play?

00:13:48.329 --> 00:13:50.230 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
She's a natural mother!

00:13:50.864 --> 00:13:53.300 position:16% line:83% align:start
The kids are drawn to her
so effortlessly.

00:13:53.735 --> 00:13:55.336 position:7% line:89% align:start
She's down right Madonna-like!

00:13:55.836 --> 00:13:57.304 position:16% line:89% align:start
But it's more than that.

00:13:58.038 --> 00:14:00.508 position:35% line:83% align:start
Hey, Honey.
Tell me about your day.

00:14:00.775 --> 00:14:02.142 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Her wife factor.

00:14:02.644 --> 00:14:03.745 position:44% line:89% align:start
Peak!

00:14:04.078 --> 00:14:07.448 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Do your job.
-I know! I'm doing it, okay?

00:14:08.282 --> 00:14:10.017 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] So, what do you
guys wanna play now?

00:14:10.150 --> 00:14:11.352 position:38% line:83% align:start
[BOY 10D]
I'll think of what to play!

00:14:11.686 --> 00:14:13.788 position:16% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] He broke the ice
like it was nothing.

00:14:14.154 --> 00:14:15.824 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's Shinozaki for you.

00:14:15.956 --> 00:14:17.491 position:27% line:89% align:start
My capable kohai.

00:14:17.891 --> 00:14:19.393 position:7% line:89% align:start
There's something else though?

00:14:20.027 --> 00:14:21.596 position:27% line:89% align:start
He's so paternal!

00:14:22.463 --> 00:14:24.465 position:19% line:83% align:start
Look at all the smiles
on those kids.

00:14:24.632 --> 00:14:27.101 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's like he's some kind of
super-dad!

00:14:27.802 --> 00:14:29.303 position:10% line:89% align:start
But it's more than just that.

00:14:30.572 --> 00:14:31.606 position:24% line:89% align:start
Welcome home, hun.

00:14:32.206 --> 00:14:34.041 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
His husband factor.

00:14:34.408 --> 00:14:35.342 position:44% line:89% align:start
Peak!

00:14:35.476 --> 00:14:37.512 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:14:37.746 --> 00:14:39.480 position:24% line:89% align:start
Aah! Oh hey, kids!

00:14:39.647 --> 00:14:41.882 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, what do you want
to play next?

00:14:42.015 --> 00:14:45.052 position:30% line:83% align:start
