if you don't let go!

00:14:48.389 --> 00:14:50.592 position:7% line:89% align:start
You let go of him first, Marin!

00:14:50.891 --> 00:14:52.159 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
Hey, play nice.

00:14:52.292 --> 00:14:54.094 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's enough
for everybody here!

00:14:54.428 --> 00:14:56.330 position:7% line:89% align:start
Look, see! This one's for you.

00:14:56.531 --> 00:14:59.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
