playing by herself

00:15:01.368 --> 00:15:02.871 position:16% line:89% align:start
instead of with everyone.

00:15:03.237 --> 00:15:04.304 position:19% line:89% align:start
You noticed that, huh?

00:15:04.773 --> 00:15:06.775 position:13% line:83% align:start
-You should play with her.
-[blushing]

00:15:07.274 --> 00:15:09.009 position:16% line:83% align:start
