00:15:23.825 --> 00:15:25.058 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow!

00:15:25.225 --> 00:15:26.828 position:24% line:83% align:start
You know, we'd like
to play with you too

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.362 position:16% line:89% align:start
