00:15:34.736 --> 00:15:36.571 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-You can be the daddy, okay?

00:15:36.871 --> 00:15:39.607 position:21% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] If Shinozaki
is the daddy, then.

00:15:39.808 --> 00:15:42.109 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh. And you can be.

00:15:42.677 --> 00:15:45.045 position:27% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Oh boy,
