but he's my kohai.

00:15:56.190 --> 00:15:57.424 position:27% line:89% align:start
No that's wrong!

00:15:57.559 --> 00:16:00.562 position:24% line:83% align:start
Mommy doesn't call
daddy kohai, just Daddy!

00:16:01.261 --> 00:16:03.397 position:13% line:89% align:start
Okay. I guess that's true.

00:16:04.998 --> 00:16:06.500 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're her parents.

00:16:06.634 --> 00:16:08.135 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes, her parents.

00:16:09.269 --> 00:16:11.739 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yay! Daddy! Mommy!

00:16:12.540 --> 00:16:13.575 position:35% line:89% align:start
[blushing]

00:16:13.708 --> 00:16:15.209 position:24% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] It's like
looking into the future!

00:16:15.577 --> 00:16:17.344 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I mustn't!
This is for the child,

00:16:17.478 --> 00:16:18.979 position:10% line:89% align:start
not living out my fantasies.

00:16:19.112 --> 00:16:20.515 position:27% line:89% align:start
What can you be?

00:16:21.081 --> 00:16:22.316 position:30% line:89% align:start
The kitty cat!

00:16:22.717 --> 00:16:23.918 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:24.051 --> 00:16:26.621 position:27% line:83% align:start
You be the kitty
and I can be the mommy!

00:16:27.154 --> 00:16:29.557 position:27% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] No fair,
I wanted to be the mommy.

00:16:30.257 --> 00:16:31.693 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
I guess everyone can see

00:16:31.826 --> 00:16:33.728 position:10% line:89% align:start
just how cat-like Senpai is.

00:16:33.928 --> 00:16:35.162 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
The cat?

00:16:35.329 --> 00:16:37.464 position:27% line:83% align:start
